<form name="Chooser" startPoint="true" themePath="default" process="NameEm">
<items>
<text label="T1"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="220" color="000000">Form a fantasy tennis team for the French Open by drawing from the players below. You get to choose 2 players in men's singles, 2 players in women's singles, and 3 doubles teams. You also have the option to designate a player not included in this list as your choice to win one of the singles crowns.</font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q1"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="220" color="000000">Enter your e-mail address so we can notify you if you are the winner.</font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"> </font><blank label="a" length="20" required="true" alternateLabel="email"/></paragraph></fib>
